User Stories

Doctor:
1. "I want to be able to keep record of the user’s health and monitor the pressure levels so that I can prevent ulcers"

Patient:
1. “I want to be able to login and see the pressure metrics highlighting the critical points so that I can make necessary changes"
2. “I want to be able to contact a doctor or carer so that I can get help or advice when needed”
3. "I want to recieve an alert when I am exceeded my peak pressure so that if I am asleep I can change my positon accordingly"

Carers:
1. "I want to be able to login and view the patient’s dashboard and have an idea of where the critical pressure points are so I can take that into consideration during care and provide appropriate service."
2. "I want to be able to change my patients peak pressure points so that I can adjust the sensor for their needs"
3. "I want to recieve alerts when a patient exceeds their peak pressure for a long duration of time so that I can check if they need any help"

Admin:
1. “I want to have access to the graphene trace software, to be able to monitor it’s performance, implement changes based on checks performed to ensure accuracy, and add new features when necessary”.
